Introduction

Miso, born Kim Mi-so, is a South Korean singer, producer, and DJ who debuted independently in 2016.

She is a part of the artist collective Club Eskimo, alongside DEAN, Crush, millic, punchnello, OFONOFF (Colde & 0channel), Jusen, Chek Parren, 2xxx & Rad Museum.

Miso is the older sister of singer-songwriter and composer Maddox.
